@startuml "Диаграмма развёртывания СУТ"

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam node {
    BackgroundColor #D4E6F1
    BorderColor #2E86C1
}

title Диаграмма развёртывания СУТ\n(Docker Compose)

actor "Пользователь\n(Браузер)" as User

node "Docker Host" as DH {
    node "frontend (nginx:alpine)\nПорт: 3000 → 80" as FE {
        artifact "Vue.js SPA\n(dist/)" as SPA
        artifact "nginx.conf\n(reverse proxy)" as NGX
    }

    node "backend (Debian slim)\nПорт: 5123 → 5000" as BE {
        artifact "sut_backend\n(C++17 binary)" as BIN
        component "cpp-httplib\n(HTTP server)" as HTTP
        component "libpqxx 7.8\n(PostgreSQL client)" as PQXX
        component "OpenSSL\n(PBKDF2 hashing)" as SSL
    }

    node "db (postgres:16-alpine)\nПорт: 5432" as PGNODE {
        database "PostgreSQL 16\nБД: sut\nПользователь: sut_user" as PG {
            storage "users" as T1
            storage "projects" as T2
            storage "requirements" as T3
            storage "requirement_history" as T4
            storage "trace_links" as T5
            storage "change_requests" as T6
            storage "baselines" as T7
            storage "notifications" as T8
            storage "audit_log" as T9
        }
    }

    FE -[hidden]right- BE
    BE -[hidden]right- PGNODE
}

User --> FE : HTTP :3000
FE --> BE : proxy /api/*\n→ backend:5000
BE --> PGNODE : libpqxx\nTCP :5432

note bottom of FE
    **Сборка фронтенда:**
    1. node:20-alpine → npm install + build
    2. nginx:alpine → копирование dist/
    **Конфигурация nginx:**
    - / → try_files → index.html (SPA)
    - /api/ → proxy_pass backend:5000
end note

note bottom of BE
    **Сборка бэкенда:**
    1. gcc:13 → CMake + make
    2. debian:bookworm-slim → копирование бинаря
    **Зависимости (CMake FetchContent):**
    - cpp-httplib (header-only)
    - nlohmann/json (header-only)
    - libpqxx (system package)
    - OpenSSL (system package)
end note

note bottom of PGNODE
    **Данные:**
    Volume: pgdata
    Healthcheck: pg_isready
    Миграции: run_migrations()
    (CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS)
end note

@enduml
